  "text": "In this new environment, Beaufort International Ltd (Beaufort) has turned to new concepts and techniques in an attempt to understand these new markets from a different perspective. In particular we have begun to employ agentbased modelling (ABM) techniques as an exciting new approach to modelling customer and market behaviour. Conceptually, this work is partly derived from the new interdisciplinary movement known as the``Science of complexity'' (Waldrop, 1994; [CITATION_1] . In the natural, biological and social sciences, complexity ideas are being",
